While good samaritans continue to donate food aid to flood victims in KZN there are concerns these donations are not reaching the intended people. Some communities have raised the alarm. eNCA’s Lethiwe Mdluli has the details. #eNCA #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - There are concerns that relief aid for victims of the KwaZulu-Natal floods are being stolen. READ: KZN floods | ANC NEC to hand over donations to flood victims Communities say donated food and clothing are just not reaching them. Thousands of people were left destitute in April following floods in the province.